# XSS (Cross-site scripting)

## Utilities 
- [**Online**] [Xsshunter](https://xsshunter.com/) XSS Hunter allows you to find all kinds of cross-site scripting vulnerabilities, including the often-missed blind XSS. The service works by hosting specialized XSS probes which, upon firing, scan the page and send information about the vulnerable page to the XSS Hunter service.
